# Normalize ALL text files to LF in the repo (README, configs, docs, ...) — and
# shell scripts + git hooks MUST stay LF on every OS, or a CRLF shebang (\r) breaks
# them on macOS/Linux (and Git Bash). Do not change this.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh            text eol=lf
githooks/*      text eol=lf
.githooks/*     text eol=lf
